‚ùóÔ∏è Important Reminder ‚ùóÔ∏è

‚ù?There is NO official Binance Customer Support on Discord.

‚õîÔ∏è Anyone that claims to be Binance Customer Service and messages you first in a private message is a scammer. If anyone asks you to send money to any address, they are also trying to scam you and should be ignored. Please report these users immediately.

üòá Our Binance Angels are moderators of this server and can point you to the right resources, but they don't provide technical support. Angels will not PM you first. Beware of imposters.

‚û°Ô∏è If you are in need of assistance, you can reach out to our Live Chat Support Team by Tapping üëâ Here! (https://www.binance.com/en/chat)
If you are still confused regarding how to contact Support, See this How-To üëâ Video (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-VelozCwX28&t=5s)
You may also want to read how the New support system works (https://www.binance.com/en/support/announcement/c5554bd4a2d8434082f4f9a08a524c8b)

Reminder:

The Binance Discord Server is a platform for discussion.
- Advertising coins or projects unaffiliated with Binance CEX result in a kick/ban.
- Offensive imagery/language > Ban
- Animated emoji spammer will be muted/kicked/banned (As the case may be)
- Massive shilling (rockets, moon) and senseless dropping of coin names will be punished also.
- No PM, DM, message me
- No trading advice. No buy ABC, no sell XYZ.
- No links to groups/websites unrelated to Binance.

Thank you and happy chatting!
